# Cloudflare Pages headers. Applies to every response.
# NOTE: each header value must be a single line. CSP is long by necessity.
#
# CSP rationale (origins actually used by this site):
#   challenges.cloudflare.com → Turnstile (script + iframe)
#   unpkg.com                 → Leaflet CSS (style-src only; Flock is self-hosted)
#   cdn.jsdelivr.net          → DuckDB-WASM bundles + blob worker (importScripts)
#   *.tinybird.co             → analytics read/ingest + Flock
#   {auth,internal,api,lake}.electiondata.my → auth Worker, i18n/R2, public API, parquet data lake
#   api/events.mapbox.com     → Mapbox GL tiles + telemetry
#   fonts.googleapis/gstatic  → Google Fonts
# 'unsafe-inline' (script) is required by the inline theme script + Astro's
# hydration bootstrap; static hosting can't issue per-request nonces. The hard
# clickjacking control here is frame-ancestors 'none' (+ X-Frame-Options).
# 'wasm-unsafe-eval' + blob workers are required by DuckDB-WASM and Mapbox GL.
#
# CSP is now enforcing. Violations are blocked (not just logged).
# Clickjacking is additionally enforced via X-Frame-Options (independent of CSP).
#
# Notes on removed directives:
#   browsing-topics        → removed from Permissions-Policy; Chrome no longer
#                            recognises this feature name (it was renamed before standardisation).
#   upgrade-insecure-reqs → removed from CSP; meaningless in report-only mode
#                            (it's an action directive, not a restriction — browsers ignore it).
#   static.cloudflareinsights.com → added to script-src; Cloudflare Pages injects
#                            the beacon automatically and it must be explicitly allowed.

/*
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=()
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=63072000; includeSubDomains
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; base-uri 'self'; object-src 'none'; frame-ancestors 'none'; form-action 'self'; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' 'wasm-unsafe-eval' https://challenges.cloudflare.com https://cdn.jsdelivr.net https://static.cloudflareinsights.com; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://fonts.googleapis.com https://unpkg.com; img-src 'self' data: blob: https:; font-src 'self' data: https://fonts.gstatic.com; connect-src 'self' https://auth.electiondata.my https://internal.electiondata.my https://api.electiondata.my https://lake.electiondata.my https://api.us-west-2.aws.tinybird.co https://api.mapbox.com https://events.mapbox.com https://cdn.jsdelivr.net https://cloudflareinsights.com; worker-src 'self' blob:; child-src 'self' blob:; frame-src https://challenges.cloudflare.com; manifest-src 'self'
